# Shot On Me & Venue Portal

An innovative social payment platform connecting friends and venues.

## üöÄ Quick Start

### Option 1: Automated Setup (Windows)
```powershell
.\setup.ps1
```

### Option 2: Manual Setup

1. **Backend:**
```bash
cd backend
npm install
npm run dev
```

2. **Venue Portal:**
```bash
cd venue-portal
npm install
npm run dev
```

3. **Shot On Me App:**
```bash
cd shot-on-me
npm install
npm run dev
```

